text: Fejér is a Hungarian-language surname. It may refer to: *Andor Fejér (born 1960), Hungarian electrical engineer and politician *András Fejér (born 1955), Hungarian cellist *Jules Fejer (1914 - 2002), Hungarian physicist *George Fejer ( (Hungarian: Fejér György) (1766 – 1851), Hungarian author and cleric *George Feyer, born György Fejér (1921 - 1977), Canadian cartoonist *George Feyer (pianist), born György Fejér (1908 - 2001) *Géza Fejér (1945), Hungarian discus thrower *Lipót Fejér (1880 - 1959), Hungarian mathematician *Tamás Fejér (1920 – 2006), Hungarian film director ==See also== *Feyer (surname) Category:Hungarian-language surnames
